00:27:30.060 --> 00:27:31.050
like.

00:27:31.050 --> 00:27:34.120
And if they are so different,
what can we say about it?

00:27:34.120 --> 00:27:36.570
Is there any way we
can predict earthquakes

00:27:36.570 --> 00:27:41.100
or the size of the earthquake
