[INAUDIBLE] just on
plate boundaries.

00:33:24.940 --> 00:33:27.440
Earthquakes happen
in unforeseen places,

00:33:27.440 --> 00:33:30.400
so we can't really just
predict an earthquake tomorrow,

00:33:30.400 --> 00:33:32.860
but these are the
earthquakes that remind us

00:33:32.860 --> 00:33:34.630
how young our field is.

